<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Roomie Booking</h1>
    <p>
      Hi all, and welcome to Roomie booking! <%= @users_names.to_sentence %> have requested a booking,
      and <%= @listing.owner.first_name %> has accepted.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here are the booking details:</br>
      Listing: <%= @listing.title %> (<%= url_for @listing %>)</br>
      Start: <%= @start_date.to_formatted_s(:short) %></br>
      End: <%= @end_date.to_formatted_s(:short) %>
    </p>
    <p>
      Please keep me in the loop and use this email chain to take care of any arrangements, lease signing, and payment confirmations.</br>
      That way we can ensure all of you have a great experience!
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for using Roomie and have a great day!</br>
    The Roomie team.</p>
  </body>
</html>
